data.description: Welcome to 1803 Hamilton Creek Trail this home has acreage & NOT in a HOA + with landscaping already done! This home is for YOU! Be in "awe" of the 10' ceilings as you walk into the formal living room that is adjacent to an office/den area. In the family room you'll be welcomed to an open floor plan to the beautiful kitchen with granite counters, breakfast bar, gas range, & great cabinet/counter space, including a pantry! Check out those custom fitted wood shutters on the windows, hardwood Flooring + Tile! Main suite features Double door entry + sliding exterior door & amazing natural light. Master Bath offers a shower stall + a separate soaker tub, double sinks & a walk-in closet. The other 3 bedrooms are great sized! The outside is spectacular! Full wood fencing, grass with auto-sprinklers, rock + oversized concrete patio. Full stucco exterior! The icing on the cake is that amazing 4 car garage! Elko city views from the front + easy location to downtown & hills for play time on the toys. Hamilton Stage subdivision is where it's at for easy living in a newer community. Upgraded water softener & reverse osmosis system!
